{"tid":2380553,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人妻驚見老公與女子同遊照 怒斬「偷食夫」後始知屬自己舊照","createTime":"2021-01-26T03:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T05:40:03.000Z","uid":56321,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"943bfbd233526f9ae215da221cc02bdc9714e69a","tid":2380553,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:32:54.000Z","msg":"墨西哥索諾拉一名人妻於丈夫手機發現與另一名女性遊玩的相片，認定丈夫出軌，怒斬丈夫。但她事後竟發現相片中的是多年前的自己。<br />\n<br />\n據當地媒體報道，里歐諾拉發現丈夫胡安手機內存有多張與一名年輕女子出遊的相片，但未有認出相中人是自己，更誤會他出軌，於是憤怒下拿起菜刀斬傷丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n胡安被斬傷後，忍痛向妻子解釋相片是二人未結婚時所拍的，只是近日將舊照片重新存入手機。<br />\n<br />\n鄰居於事發後聽到慘叫聲，故幫忙報警，警方其後到場處理，而胡安身上有多處刀傷，其妻里歐諾拉則於22日被當地警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1983279/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1983279%2F&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=08581ab2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1983279%2F&h=3cadf828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1983279/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己都認唔到"},{"pid":"f14341cc27b58b4e93e33607e1c296790437a4da","tid":2380553,"uid":242537,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"所以話 化妝真係恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfac5e9372c27acb55981cad480be5087454cef","tid":2380553,"uid":183844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"老公個樣咁多年無變?"},{"pid":"bf4529b3b0938eaf246bf81702077c731186587e","tid":2380553,"uid":92383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas